reviews.text: Classic Bar Pacific in a quiet area, along with Billboard and Dart.

Walked in at 7pm as we have just moved to the area and thought we'd try it out. It's a very strange bar.  Only a few people there. No welcome from the surly barman who put an ipad on the table and said there's the menu. We couldn't get it to work...had to ask him. Expensive prices.

People were smoking inside. Table was sticky/dirty. Loud Chinese karaoke on every screen. No happy hour or wine by the glass.  We left.
